---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Sergei Rastrigin" description="Software engineer based in the UK, building developer tools and AI agent infrastructure.">
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-text)] via-[var(--color-accent)] to-[var(--color-secondary)] bg-clip-text text-transparent">
      About
    </h1>
  </section>

  <article class="prose">
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Sergei. I'm exploring AI agents and building tools around them. This blog
      is where I share what I learn.
      <a href="https://github.com/rastrigin-systems/arfa" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">Arfa</a>
      is the first one.
    </p>

  </article>
</Layout>
